name: High-5
description:
We're using machine-learning algorithms to teach our AI how to high-five each other. Will you help us?

Controls

Spacebar/Enter: Start

Spacebar: Stop right robot's meters

Enter: Stop left robot's meters

Best played with two players. Refresh the webpage to try again.
